{"tid":1557442,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今日3點鐘，9up議政巴組織既‘保障民生建設聯盟’將會舉行記者會","createTime":"2019-09-10T06:11:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T10:38:28.000Z","uid":48083,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fa224081a3a7204fa2a4843a84d36d1d9657f7f9","tid":1557442,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:11:40.000Z","msg":"各位傳媒朋友：<br />\n謹代表保障民生建設聯盟（「保民聯」），誠摯邀請 貴機構／閣下出席以下的傳媒招待會：<br />\n主題：保障民生建設聯盟成立傳媒招待會<br />\n- 保民聯成立宗旨及背景<br />\n- 九大政策倡議<br />\n- 2019年區議會選舉參選意向<br />\n日期：2019年9月10日（星期二）<br />\n時間：下午2時45分 - \u0016傳媒登\u0016記<br />\n下午3時正 - 傳媒招待會<br />\n語言：廣東話<br />\n<br />\n關於保障民生建設聯盟<br />\n保障民生建設聯盟（「保民聯」或「聯盟」）於2019年9月成立，並提出「一心保民，世代同行」為其創黨綱領。保民聯由一眾愛國愛港的年青力量所組成，立志以保障民生經濟為政綱重心，務求擺脫「敵我矛盾」的對立思維，讓老中青三代攜手同行，促進社會和諧、繁榮及穩定。聯盟主張貫徹落實「一國兩制」主義方針，依據基本法規定堅定落實「港人治港」、「高度自治」，維護香港核心價值，為國家提供制度的對沖優勢，使香港在國家開放、改革中都可作出具體且有力的貢獻。聯盟的使命是監察政府施政，公平公正的方針落實利民政策，持續提高施政水平及效率。<br />\n<br />\n招待會亦已預留公眾席，有興趣市民請於以下連結先行登記，如成功登記將會由專人聯絡：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/1RjrBcXmeyjWLxsh6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F1RjrBcXmeyjWLxsh6&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=680f363e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/1RjrBcXmeyjWLxsh6</a><br />\n<br />\n如欲取得更多聯盟相關資料，請瀏覽網站及Facebook專頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://HKASEA.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2FHKASEA.org%2F&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=5b37446d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://HKASEA.org/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ASEA2019/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FASEA2019%2F&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=dc1dfadb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ASEA2019/</a><br />\n屆時亦會有於本Facebook專頁進行直播，謝謝！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1548898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1548898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n敬希垂注<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5947f8f2955fd174ea191bfd6a260119429b551b","tid":1557442,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f096dbda45a31ea7b37aa6be70ea7d2b7633d547","tid":1557442,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:14:40.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n新活動：唱民主聖歌，傳福音！<br />\n手足每晚都好努力貼連儂，但凌晨3-6就比人清！<br />\n913 914 915 活動要去，但請起返連儂牆<br />\n<ins>考驗毅力與堅持</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">做更具價值嘅野</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">等所有人知道發生緊咩事先！</span></span></strong><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">連儂牆起源於反共，呢條戰線不能倒！</code></pre><br />\n勇武走得太前，做人要有公關！<br />\n文宣多一個就好多！連儂牆要人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一場抗爭/革命搞十年八載唔出奇<br />\n<strong>衛城革命，生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">幫襯</span>良心小店<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">抵制</span>「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n3. 安全之下，<span style=\"color: red;\">免費港鐵</span>；二人同遊，一人免費；買平飛；長者八達通<br />\n4. 夜晚<span style=\"color: red;\">十點吶喊</span>！！！連繫左鄰右里<br />\n5. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\">每日一post</span>，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=a91358c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n7. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n8. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會事務，做陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.10"},{"pid":"89d6b52503f99c18852a9388ad6f2ed4aa4a39f5","tid":1557442,"uid":202735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:16:05.000Z","msg":"支持愛國愛港力量 我們不要暴力"},{"pid":"9ecf7a122a7e12e1fbcf55942b6d68062874f0a7","tid":1557442,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:17:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7790b18c355bec6f609effdd3d3bf27c07b06dc7","tid":1557442,"uid":203322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:17:15.000Z","msg":"支持深藍政黨"},{"pid":"dfcc50f66f022b19be74a6aa62e3953c657fb30d","tid":1557442,"uid":20979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"35a9b0cdf0b5435a8c8dd7baa55bd15b6b40db4f","tid":1557442,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:16:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"479906d25f3ac2ae0a67c735f0ed79deeaf7eaee","tid":1557442,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:19:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/videos/live/m/redirect/443420146265861/?refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FASEA2019%2Fvideos%2F443420146265861%2F&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fvideos%2Flive%2Fm%2Fredirect%2F443420146265861%2F%3Frefsrc%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fm.facebook.com%252FASEA2019%252Fvideos%252F443420146265861%252F%26_rdr&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=9c876042\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/videos/live/m/redirect/443420146265861/?refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FASEA2019%2Fvideos%2F443420146265861%2F&amp;_rdr</a>"},{"pid":"4a842839ce29b05a079a5b0a013b350b81d3ee53","tid":1557442,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971e93659cdc9ccf99151571a19668d3ab8084b1","tid":1557442,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:21:13.000Z","msg":"真愛聯d fd ?"},{"pid":"3c714a70f901925bddda19c27d6b255d6e691b05","tid":1557442,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:24:03.000Z","msg":"同民主黨記招撞時間<br />\n有信報記者算係咁"},{"pid":"d4d0ba7b9aade4a365c77fa9bc33f5e03f575745","tid":1557442,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:25:50.000Z","msg":"P 俾超額發唔到Post，please help <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">9.15 係「國際民主日」，點解完全無活動Post? </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根據《世界人權宣言》第二十一條第（三）款﹕「人民的意志是政府權力的基礎」<br />\n9.15係聯合國嘅「國際民主日」，2019年主題「參與」，重申民主係「以人為中心」。(官網﹕<a href=\"https://www.un.org/zh/events/democracyday/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fzh%2Fevents%2Fdemocracyday%2F&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=34dd0290\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.un.org/zh/events/democracyday/</a> (得殘體字sorry) ) <br />\n<br />\n我哋依定係對抗緊極權，爭取緊雙普選，呢個咁有象徵意義嘅日子點可以唔做嘢? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">本地應該要搞大遊行，本來民陣前兩日都話申請緊</span>，但警方唔回應就完全無哂聲氣。<span style=\"color: red;\">海外集會要再次港、藏、疆合作</span>，甚至聯繫埋全世界受壓迫地區嘅人一齊發聲。<br />\n<br />\n6.12、721、811、831&hellip;全部都要勝利之後先可以查明真相，如果唔係有再多嘅證據，未來都只會變成野史。請大家化憤怒為創意同行動吧！世界領袖讚賞我哋嘅，係呢場運動嘅靈活多變，不忘同世界連軌。而我地亦已成功將呢場運動變成<span style=\"color: red;\">自由世界VS極權嘅抗爭</span>。我哋唔想成為國際怨婦，就要令更加多人明白This is <span style=\"color: red;\">NOT ONLY a protest for Hong Kong people but for the sake of the World! </span><br />\n<br />\nAttention! 依家正苦係咁用衝突黎分化我哋同世界建立既信任。請大家要好小心好小心好小心好小心好小心好小心! <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Free Hong Kong <br />\nAnti Chinazi </span></span><br />\n<br />\nP.S. <br />\n1. 之前有巴打寫﹕If we burn, the world burns  有無人留咗record ? <br />\n2. 回顧9.4 「2019年中美關係回顧」聽證會<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-09-05/70001880\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2019-09-05%2F70001880&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=3fd5ac2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-09-05/70001880</a>"},{"pid":"9d6de5a8d2f2b13ec5fecb387958e16678a9b1bc","tid":1557442,"uid":35229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:30:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/inmediahk/videos/480739942780101/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Finmediahk%2Fvideos%2F480739942780101%2F&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=4e4dc21d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/inmediahk/videos/480739942780101/</a>"},{"pid":"02de41f113c8dd9584b8c95ecb166cdc1ad868ab","tid":1557442,"uid":62807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:33:55.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"407e190b4d0b55af184f8fc911bc1b64d0cd5432","tid":1557442,"uid":191290,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gcwkjez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGcwkjez.png&h=71e8f36a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋好厲害忍辱負重<br />\n睇吓啲留言你哋開個頭開得好靚"},{"pid":"116f59d69960b463fe7955893caa066c7148b5c8","tid":1557442,"uid":56248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl